label: FDN2300
info_inclusion: Press and hold the top button for 3 seconds min and release when beep is heard to signify the device has been included into the network.
info_exclusion: Press and hold the top button for 3 seconds min and release when beep is heard to signify the device has been excluded from the network.
category_description: Any device attached to the wall that controls a binary status of something, for ex. a light switch

commandclass.name: NO_OPERATION
commandclass.label: No Operation - used for PINGing a device.
